OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FCompensation for customers receiving
OL,7,Fpoor services from water companies who
OL,8,Fare failing to meet standards could
OL,9,Fmore than double under new Government
OL,10,Fproposals.
OL,12,FAs part of the plans, the list of
OL,13,Fcircumstances that can trigger
OL,14,Fcompensation will also be expanded,
OL,15,Fincluding automatic payments for those
OL,16,Fissued boil notices or when water
OL,17,Fcompanies fail to conduct meter
OL,18,Freadings or installations as promised.
