OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said
OL,7,Fthe Government hopes to "turn the tide
OL,8,Fon the destruction of our waterways".
OL,10,FThe proposals, which will be subject
OL,11,Fto an eight-week consultation, will
OL,12,Fincrease the amount of reimbursement
OL,13,Fthat customers are legally entitled to
OL,14,Fwhen standards are not met by water
OL,15,Fcompanies.
