OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FFor households impacted by an
OL,7,Fincorrect notice of planned supply
OL,8,Finterruption, compensation will rise
OL,9,Ffrom #20 to #50, meanwhile
OL,10,Freimbursement for internal flooding
OL,11,Ffrom sewers will increase from a
OL,12,Fmaximum of #1,000 to #2,000.
OL,14,FEarlier this year, around 16,000
OL,15,Fresidents of Brixham, Devon, were left
OL,16,Fwithout tap water for eight weeks, and
OL,17,Fwere told to boil their water before
OL,18,Fdrinking it, cooking with it, or
OL,19,Fbrushing their teeth.
