OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FIf the compensation changes had been
OL,7,Fin place when the outages occurred,
OL,8,Fthe residents would have automatically
OL,9,Fbeen entitled to payments. But the
OL,10,FGovernment has said the regulations
OL,11,Fwill not apply retrospectively.
OL,13,FAnnouncing the proposals, Mr Reed
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our water industry is broken.
OL,15,FAfter years of failure, households and
OL,16,Fbusinesses have been let down by water
OL,17,Fcompanies time and time again.
