OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FJenny Suggate, director of policy,
OL,7,Fresearch and campaigns at CCW, said:
OL,8,F"We're delighted the Government is
OL,9,Ffast-tracking efforts to improve the
OL,10,FGuaranteed Standards Scheme, with the
OL,11,Fpotential to boost compensation and
OL,12,Fsupport for hundreds of thousands of
OL,13,Fpeople each year when they are let
OL,14,Fdown by their water company.
OL,16,F"Given that there has been little
OL,17,Fchange to the standards since they
OL,18,Fwere first introduced, an overhaul is
OL,19,Flong overdue, and we know it is a
OL,20,Fpressing priority for household and
OL,21,Fbusiness customers.
