OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,F"Demanding higher standards of service
OL,7,Fand improving levels of compensation
OL,8,Fwhen things go wrong will incentivise
OL,9,Fwater companies to get things right
OL,10,Fthe first time for all customers."
OL,12,FThe Guaranteed Standards Scheme, which
OL,13,Fcovers timely restoration of water
OL,14,Fsupply following an interruption,
OL,15,Fresponding to written complaints, and
OL,16,Fmanaging the risk of sewer flooding,
OL,17,Fis being updated for the first time
OL,18,Fsince 2000.
