OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FThis comes as water companies face
OL,7,Fcriticism for their handling of
OL,8,Fsewage, with Ofwat proposing #168
OL,9,Fmillion of fines for three of
OL,10,FEngland's biggest water companies.
OL,12,FThe penalties include a #104 million
OL,13,Fpenalty for Thames Water, #47 million
OL,14,Fpenalty for Yorkshire Water and #17
OL,15,Fmillion for Northumbrian Water for
OL,16,Ffailing to manage sewage spills.
OL,18,FThe Government has previously
OL,19,Fannounced a Water (Special Measures)
OL,20,FBill to cut sewage spills and attract
OL,21,Finvestment to upgrade infrastructure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
