OL,3,CCompensation for water customers to
OL,4,Cdouble in government crackdown
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat Environment
OL,7,Fspokesperson Tim Farron MP said of
OL,8,Fplans to boost compensation: "We will
OL,9,Fscrutinise these proposals closely and
OL,10,Fwelcome any attempts to crack down on
OL,11,Fthese greedy firms but make no
OL,12,Fmistake, our water industry needs top
OL,13,Fto bottom reform.
OL,15,F"That must start with abolishing Ofwat
OL,16,Fand replacing it with a new regulator
OL,17,Fwith real teeth to clampdown on these
OL,18,Fpolluting firms, end the sewage
OL,19,Fscandal and get bill payers the fair
OL,20,Fdeal they deserve."
